Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.72,0:15:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet the source of that very materiality\Nwithout God there would nothing nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.68,0:15:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing would be\Nwell that's scary is it
