Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.75,0:16:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,when you realize that even the toad is a\Ncreation of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.04,0:16:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So all that is is nothing exists except\Nthat which has been created by God.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.44,0:16:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,God is the sole source of existence and\Nthe potentiality of beingness. God is
