Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.76,0:40:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You can only some guy was going to jump\Noff the Empire State Building and they
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.28,0:40:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,made him they buckled him to the\Nbuilding. Remember that? Yeah. He was
