Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.48,0:41:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,to move from\Nbeing
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.64,0:41:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,to know that you are.\NTo be is one thing to know that you are
