Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.59,0:42:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mostly that which exists does so and did\Nnot realize that it exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.00,0:42:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,To exist and know that you exist makes\Nyou enlightened.
