Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.83,0:43:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody here that doesn't know that they\Nare?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.68,0:43:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Get my gun. Get me.\NIt's not possible to be here and not
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.68,0:43:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,know that you are. The fact that you're\Nhere means you know that you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.31,0:43:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore,\Nthere's no point in seeking
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.48,0:43:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,enlightenment because you already are.\NSo, the trick between the unenlightened
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.59,0:43:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and the enlightened is merely knowing\Nthe difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.56,0:43:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The unenlightened doesn't know that\Nthey're enlightened already and
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.68,0:43:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,therefore they're unenlightened.\NThe enlightened knows that they're
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.11,0:43:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,enlightened already and therefore is\Nenlightened. Wow.
